

Xverse is widely considered one of the top choices for Stacks. It works on Android, iOS, and as a browser extension, and offers a clean, user-friendly interface. It lets you manage STX, BTC, and sBTC, participate in stacking and delegated stacking pools, interact with dApps, and view NFTs directly in the wallet.
